        "about-body": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Framelight is a small working studio run by a single photographer. The work is editorial in spirit — warm, observed, and shaped around the subject rather than the camera. Every project begins with a conversation and ends with prints you can hold.</p>",
